title: S12 Ep226: Expect the Extraordinary: Angelic Messages, Spiritual Encounters
itunes:title: Expect the Extraordinary: Angelic Messages, Spiritual Encounters
description:
Sue Pighini knows what it is like to have been struck by lightning; when it happened to her at age 28, her clothes melted. She also knows what it is like to survive cancer, a brain aneurysm and to be held-up at gunpoint. All of those experiences, as one might imagine, led her to live her life differently.

Sue will explain what an angel is, how everyone has their own angels, and how to communicate with them for guidance.

PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind Darkness Dave shares his a real life Christmas Miracle.
